msgstr "TVGate 管理配置"

msgid "Tips"
msgstr "使用提示"

msgid "On first install, download and start the TVGate binary."
msgstr "首次安装请先下载并启动 TVGate 二进制。"

msgid "Then configure and save settings on this page."
msgstr "随后在此页面完善并保存配置。"

msgid "After saving the configuration, verify that the changes have taken effect."
msgstr "保存配置后,确认修改已生效。"

